# Repository-wide Trivy ignores (misconfigs, secrets false positives, accepted risks).

# AVD-DS-0031 flags Dockerfile ENV names that look like credentials. This image
# intentionally declares empty defaults for runtime injection (RESTIC_PASSWORD*,
# OpenStack OS_*); values are not baked into layers as secrets.
AVD-DS-0031
DS-0031

# AVD-DS-0002 (non-root USER): This helper builds on restic/restic and runs
# crond, optional FUSE mounts, and NFS client mounts as root—switching to an
# unprivileged user would break typical deployments; mitigate with read-only
# sources, minimal caps, and orchestrator policies instead.
AVD-DS-0002
DS-0002
